name: Fruitcraft app, a Trading Card Game with Fruit warriors
blurb: Join Fruitcraft app, a "Clash of Clan" style trading card game. Build your army, band with friends and squish your foe.

rewards.reward: (~$7) The app + high res booklet of all the characters + a thank you on Twitter.

THANK YOU, CARVED IN PIXELS (~$15):\r\nWelcome to Fruitcraft's hall of fame. You will receive everything from the previous level. Also you will receive early access to Fruitcraft on other platforms that we might invade... think Andoid, Web, Desktop and maybe even Ouya!\r\n(Thank you + hall of fame + early game access)

THANK YOU, FRUITCRAFTER (~30):\r\nAs a true fan, you will get everything from the previous levels and an exclusive invite to the Kickstarter Tribe on Fruitcraft, giving you battle and defence bonus. Let\u2019s see if anyone can mess with you now!\r\n(Thank you + hall of fame + early game access + Kickstarter Tribe on Fruitcraft)

THANK YOU, FRIEND (~$45):\r\nIt feels like a virtual thank you wouldn\u2019t be enough. So on top of everything above, you'll be getting a personal postcard from your favourite Fruit warrior to say thank you. Who knows, maybe you could become pen pals!!\r\n(Thank you + hall of fame + early game access + Kickstarter Tribe on Fruitcraft + personal postcard)
